snippet.title: Classic Rides Collection | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Classic Rides Collection is available now to purchase for PC: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1061350/Planet_Coaster__Classic_Rides_Collection

Inspired by some of the most iconic and classic attractions from fairgrounds and theme parks around the world, Classic Rides Collection comes to Planet Coaster to add a touch of nostalgia and class to your park. This collection includes nine new rides and coasters with one variant.

For more news and information about Planet Coaster:
Website: https://planetcoaster.com/ 
Forums: https://forums.planetcoaster.com/ 
Facebook: https://facebook.com/PlanetCoaster 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlanetCoaster
